issue.title: Add outstanding models for RobotX competition

content.raw:
Question about the symbols: I see that they appear in different configurations. 

* The 2016 dock uses it: http://www.northropgrumman.com/MediaResources/MediaKits/RobotXChallenge/PublishingImages/lg_photo1_day6.jpg

* The 2016 "detect and deliver" task (see figure that Kevin attached in this issue) with holes to do some object manipulation.

Is there any other instance in which the symbols appear? Do the dock bays always have a symbol?
